stream \- John McCalpin's STREAM benchmark
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B stream
[
.I "-M <len>"
]
[
.I "-W <warmups>"
]
[
.I "-N <repetitions>"
]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B stream
mimics John McCalpin's STREAM benchmark.  It measures memory bandwidth.
.SH BUGS
.B stream
is an experimental benchmark, but it seems to work well on most
systems.  
